headline: Sequoia Strategy’s Outlook on Accenture Plc (ACN)
summary: Ruane, Cunniff LP, an investment adviser managing Sequoia Strategy, released its Q4 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. Sequoia Strategy returned 9% in Q4 compared to 2.7% for the S&P 500 Index. The Strategy delivered a return of 21.9% in 2025 versus 17.9% for the Index. In a year […]

headline: Accenture PLC (NYSE:ACN) Demonstrates a High-Quality Dividend Profile
summary: Accenture (ACN) exemplifies a quality dividend stock with a strong 2.79% yield, a history of growth, and a sustainable payout backed by robust profitability and financial health.
